Package: lite
Title: Likelihood-based Inference for Time Series Extremes
Version: 1.0.0.9000
Date: 2022-03-30
Authors@R: person(c("Paul", "J."), "Northrop", email = "p.northrop@ucl.ac.uk",
  role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Performs adjusted inferences based on model objects fitted, using 
    maximum likelihood estimation, by the extreme value analysis packages
    'exdex' <https://cran.r-project.org/package=exdex>, 
    'lax' <https://cran.r-project.org/package=lax>, 
    'revdbayes' <https://cran.r-project.org/package=revdbayes>. 
Imports: chandwich,
    exdex,
    graphics,
    revdbayes,
    sandwich,
    stats
